snippet.title: Star Wars: Movie Battles 2 - 2017 Trailer
snippet.description:
To get into the game, be sure to visit moviebattles.org!

The game is a modification of Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy, which is available on Gog.com and Steam for a fairly low price.
